mn-gap\"><code>grid-column-gap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/gap\"><code>grid-gap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css_함수","title":"CSS 함수","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/repeat\"><code>repeat()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/minmax\"><code>minmax()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/fit-content\"><code>fit-content()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css_데이터_타입","title":"CSS 데이터 타입","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/flex_value\"><code>&lt;flex&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"용어집_목록","title":"용어집 목록","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Grid (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Lines\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Grid Lines (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Tracks\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Grid Tracks (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Cell\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Grid Cell (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Areas\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Grid Area (en-US)</a